      "name": "Note: Save Conversation State",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WA_06 — Save Conversation State\n\n**Purpose:** Single atomic write path for live conversation data.\n\n**Steps:**\n1. Validate required input fields\n2. Insert message row into `conversation_messages`\n3. Update `sessions` table (live_mode only)\n4. Return success or structured error\n\n**DB tables used:**\n- `conversation_messages` — full message record\n- `sessions` — stage, CTA, escalation, qualification progress\n\n**Only runs for `session_mode = live_mode` sessions.**",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 4
      }
    }
